Estudiantes de La Plata won the championship with the following line- ups:
 
Talleres (Córdoba):     Baley (Comizzo); Festa, Galván, M.A.Oviedo, Riquelme; 
                              Lucco, Bustos, Guerini (Taborda); Ariel, R.Moreno, Reinaldi, Coleoni.
                                             Coach: Daniel A. Willington.
Estudiantes (LP):                            Delménico; Camino, Brown, Landucci, A.Herrera (Gugnali); 
                                                        M.A.Russo, J.Ponce, Trobbiani; Trama, Sabella (Lemme), Gottardi.
                                                                            Coach: Carlos S. Bilardo.
 
Goals:                  8' Brown; 24' Gottardi.
Expulsions:                52' Lucco.
Referee:                       Romero.
Stadium:                        Estadio Córdoba (Home Talleres).
Tickets:                                15.005.-
 
 
 
 
 
